## PWA Cache Versioning

When changing cached assets (HTML, CSS, JS, images, manifest), bump the cache version in `sw.js`:

```js
const CACHE_NAME = 'moto-arcade-v4';  // increment v3 → v4, etc.
```

This ensures users get fresh content on refresh instead of stale cached design.

